	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. P.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Credo, charissime in Christo domine ac praeceptor obseervande, literas istas, quas ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Gallia</placeName> d[ominationi] v[estrae] scripsi, ad manus vestras pervenisse.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum diu est, quod nihil scripti dominationi vestrae miserim, quod quidem non tam mea culpa, quam longinquę peregrinationis mora evenit, de qua ut strictim dominationi vestrae quaedam pro temporis angustia significem: 25. octobris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378">Parisiis</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301">Lugdunum</placeName> bonis avibus iter in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italiam</placeName> suscepi; primo igitur profectus sum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306">Mediolanum</placeName>, deinde per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l150">Ferrariam</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l55">Bononiam</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1098">Florentiam</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425">Romam</placeName> veni, quam sanctam appellant, sed ego [s]purcam existimo.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425">Roma</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l994">Neapolim</placeName>, postea <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1409">Anconam</placeName>, dein <placeName ref="l522">Venetias</placeName> veni bona utcunque usus fortuna, sed multa quoque adversa.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l522">Venetiis</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107">Tridentum</placeName> accessi; ibi omnia plena inveni cardinalibus, episcopis, monachis et sacerdotibus, qui quidem multa machinantur, sed nihil procedit; ipsi enim inter se discordant.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107">Tridento</placeName> per <placeName ref="l513">Ulmam</placeName> <placeName ref="l491">Argentinam</placeName>, dein <placeName ref="l157">Francfortum</placeName> veni.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eo cum venissem, statim de vestrorum omnium valetudine ex <persName ref="p1227">Froscofero</persName> petens omnia salva esse retulit, quae res mihi non parvam laetitiam attulit et maiorem, quam scribere possim.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominatio vestra hoc parvo epistolio contenta sit, oro; alias copiosius, cum tempus maius detur, scripturus.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutet, quaeso, dominatio vestra uxorem et liberos, quos deus omnipotens ad sui gloriam conservet, oro.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, praeceptor observande.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8499">Rando Schatter</persName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">1562. 24. martii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pietate ac religione praestanti viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, christianę religionis antistiti ac <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesię ministro, praeceptori suo observandissimo, hę literę.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862">Helvetio[rum]</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
